Name: popuseimapflags
Type: SWITCH
Default-Value: 0
Last-Modified: 2.3.17

If enabled, the pop server will set and obey IMAP flags.  Messages having
the \\Deleted flag are ignored as if they do not exist.  Messages that are
retrieved by the client will have the \\Seen flag set.  All messages will
have the \\Recent flag unset.
